.................... /*---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
....................  * gsm_process_command 
....................  * Parses gsm_rx_buf and acts on the command. 
....................  * 
....................  * Supported commands: 
....................  *   #ON       - Turn motor ON 
....................  *   #OF       - Turn motor OFF 
....................  *   $S        - Status query (reply to admin) 
....................  *   ?N        - Show all stored numbers (reply to admin) 
....................  *   #nX<num>  - Save number to slot X (X = 1..5), e.g. #n29876543210 
....................  *   #ENX      - Enable slot X 
....................  *   #DNX      - Disable slot X 
....................  *   @hXX      - (reserved / future use) 
....................  *---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/ 
....................  
....................  
